description: Quotient of 'base 16' division described in A032563.
maple: d:= Vector(10^7, 1):for i from 1 to 7 do   inds:= 10^i*[$1..10^(7-i)];   d[inds]:= (2*16^i+3)/5;od:b:= Vector(10^7):b[1]:= 1:for i from 2 to 10^7 do  b[i]:= b[i-1]+d[i]od: map(t-> if type(b[t]/ t,integer) then b[t]/t fi, [$1..10^7]); # _Robert Israel_, Aug 30 2015
author: _Patrick De Geest_, april 1998.
